<br>
<b>KITTIWAKE</b> chicks are now fledging at Noss. <b>30+ COMMON</a> and <b>GREY SEALS</b> at the Holm of Beosetter, and 
<b>10 COMMON SEALS</b> at Stoura Clett, East Bressay.

