Last-modified: Sat, 04 Jan 1997 23:00:14 GMT
</DOCHDR>
<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//Netscape Comm. Corp.//DTD HTML//EN">
<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Shetland News - Lady Godiva Issue 103</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY><BODY BACKGROUND="/pics/parch.gif">
<center>
<IMG SRC="/pics/header.gif">

<P>
<H1>Lady Godiva </H1>
<H2>An irregular magazine from Sanday, Orkney. </H2>
<H2>Edited by <A HREF="mailto:stockton.sanday.orkney@zetnet.co.uk">Eric Stockton</A></H2>
