<H1 ALIGN=center>
Shetland - The Old Rock for Beginners
</H1>
<H2>
or "How to go Abroad without a Passport"
</H2>
<BR>
<img SRC="/pics/ftt3.gif">

<A HREF="//www.shetland-news.co.uk/websites/bressaboats/"><img src="/bressaboats/bressaboats.jpg" hspace=2></A>

