<HEAD>
<TITLE>Shetland News - Guide to Travel Concessions 1996</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<CENTER><BODY><BODY BACKGROUND="/pics/parch.gif">
<IMG SRC="/pics/header.gif">

<H1 ALIGN=center>
Guide to Travel Concessions 1996
</H1>
<H2>
Information kindly supplied by<BR>
Shetland Council of Social Service
</H2>
</center>

<HR>


<H2>Travel Concessions WITHIN Shetland</H2>
<H3>
<ul>
<li><A HREF="withina.html">Inter Island Vehicle Ferry service</a>

<li><A HREF="withinb.html">Other Ferries</a>

<li><A HREF="withinc.html">Bus Services - all local operators</a>

<li><A HREF="withind.html">Viking Bus Station</a>

<li><A HREF="withine.html">Air Services - Inter Island Services</a>

<li><A HREF="withinf.html">Taxis and Private Hire Cars</a>
</ul>

</H3>

<HR width=70%>


<H2>Travel Concessions TO/FROM Shetland</H2>
<H3>
<ul>
<li><A HREF="outwitha1.html">P&O Ferry Services - UK Passenger Services</a>

<li><A HREF="outwitha2.html">P&O Ferry Services - UK Passenger Accompanied Cars</a>

<li><A HREF="outwithb.html">P&O Ferry Services - to Bergen, Norway</a>

<li><A HREF="outwith2.html">British Airways</a>

<li><A HREF="outwith3.html">British Airways Express - Operated by Loganair</a>

<li><A HREF="outwith4.html">Business Air</a>

<li><A HREF="external.html">UK Mainland Transport Services</a>
</ul>

</H3>

<P>
<HR>
<P>
The concessions listed are available as a right. Further information is available from the respective transport operators and your local travel agent.  <P>When actual fares are quoted, then these are expected to remain valid until at least 31st March, 1997, with the exception of P&O Scottish Ferries whose annual tariff increase is expected to take place on 1st January, 1997. 
<P>
<P>
Information kindly supplied by Shetland Council of Social Service<BR>
Brentham House, <BR>5 Harbour Street, <BR>Lerwick, ZE1 OLR.<BR>
Tel. (01595) 693816 <BR>Fax. (01595) 696787 
<P>


