<H1 ALIGN=center>
Timetables
</H1>
<H2>
when the ferries, etc. run
</H2>


</center>

<HR>
<H3>
<li><A HREF="#one">Inter-island ferry services</a>
<P>
<li><A HREF="#two">Loganair/British Airways Express - Fair Isle Service</a>
<P>
<!-- <li><A HREF="#three">Section Three - Longer articles about pollution</a>
