<A NAME="one"></a>
<H3>Inter-Island Ferry Service</H3>
<pre>
(Operated by Shetland Islands Council)

</pre>
<H3>BRESSAY FERRY crossing time 5 minutes  Ro/Ro Service </H3>
<pre>
BRESSAY 
0700 0730 0830 0850 0930 1030 1130 1245 1315 1400 1500 1600 1700 1745 1845 1930 2015 2100 2145 2230 2330* 0045* 
LERWICK 
0715 0800 0840 0900 1000 1100 1200 1300 1330 1430 1530 1630 1730 1800 1900 2000 2030 2130 2200 2300 2400* 0100* 

*Fridays and Saturdays only. 
For information during inclement weather conditions phone 01426 986763. 


</pre>
<H3>WHALSAY FERRY crossing time 30 minutes  Ro/Ro Service </H3>
<pre>
SYMBISTER
0630 0710 0750 0850 0915 1030 1115 1200 1245 1400w 1445m 1530 1615 1700 1745 1900 2115 2235* 
LAXO 
0710 0750 0830 0940 1030 1115 1200 1245 1400 1445w 1530m 1615 1700 1745 1830 2030 2200 2310* 

m = Not on Monday. w = Not on Wednesday . * = Bookings only 
Booking office open 0830 to 1300 and 1400 to 1700.  Tel. 01806 566259. 
Under certain weather conditions this service operates from Vidlin. 
At these times there may be delays. 


</pre>
<H3>YELL FERRY crossing time 20 minutes  Ro/Ro Service </H3>
<pre>
ULSTA 0630 0715 0730 0800 0820 0910 0940 1000 1040 1100 1130 1200 1230s 1330w 
TOFT  0700 0735 0755 0830 0900 0930 1000 1030 1105 1130 1200 1230 1330s 1400w 
	
ULSTA 1400s 1430w 1500s 1530w 1600 1625 1650 1725 1745 1835 1920 2040 2130 2230* 
TOFT  1430s 1500w 1525s 1555w 1625 1700 1720 1750 1810 1900 2015 2105 2200 2300* 

w = Not on Wednesday. s = Not on Sunday. * = Bookings only 
Booking office open Monday to Saturday 0830 to 1700  Tel. 01957 722259/722268. 
	

</pre>
<H3>UNST FERRY crossing time 10 minutes  Ro/Ro Service </H3>
<pre>
GUTCHER  0630 0700	0845      0930 1000 1015 1030 1100 1130 1145* 1200m 1215mo 1315m 
BELMONT  0645 0715 0825 0900 0930 1000 1015 1030      1115 1145 1200* 1215m 1230mo 1330m 

GUTCHER  1345mo l400m 1430 1500 1530s 1600 1615 1630 1700 1730 1800 1815 1900 1930 2000 2015 2100 2215 2300**
BELMONT  1400mo 1415m 1445 1530 1600  1615 1630 1645 1715 1800 1815 1830 1915 1930 2000 2030      2230 2315**

m = Not on Monday. mo = Mondays only. s = Not on Sunday. 
*= Subject to cancellation due to weather and/or mail volumes.  
** = Bookings only Th., Fr., Sa., Su. 
Booking office open Monday to Saturday 0830 to 1700  Tel. 01957 722259/722268. 


</pre>
<H3>FETLAR FERRY crossing time 25 minutes  Ro/Ro Service </H3>
<pre>
GUTCHER         0730             1030        1215m            1415th          1645      1830      2100      2300* 
BELMONT                  0825    1045                                                             2115      2315* 
ODDSTA          0755             1115        1245tho 1345m/th 1500th/s 1515so 1730      1900      2145      2345* 

* = Bookings only Th., Fr., Sa., Su. 
s = Not on Sunday. 
tho = Thursday only. 
m = Not on Monday. 
th = Not on Thursday.
s.o. = Sunday only. 
Booking office open Monday to Saturday 0830 to 1700  Tel. 01957 722259/722268. 


</pre>
<H3>SKERRIES FERRY  crossing time 90 - 120 minutes  Ro/Ro Service</H3>
<pre> 	
Monday 	              Skerries 	0800 
	              Vidlin 	0930 
Tuesday and Thursday  Skerries 	0800 	
	              Lerwick 	1445 	
Friday		      Skerries 	0800 	1130 	1600 	
	              Vidlin 	1000 	1330 	1800 
Saturday 	      Skerries 	0800 	1130 	1500 	
	              Vidlin 	1000 	1330 	1700 
Sunday	 	      Skerries 	0900 	1200 	1530 	1900 	
	              Vidlin 	1030 	1400 	1730 	 

Passengers and vehicles must be booked by 1700 on evening previous. 
When no bookings are received runs will not take place. 
All bookings to G. W. Henderson Tel. 01806 515226. 
Vehicles will only be carried weather permitting. 

</pre>
<H3>FAIR ISLE SERVICE</H3>
<pre>
2nd May - 19th September 1996

Tue/Sat/ and alternate Thu

Fair Isle d	0730
Sumburgh a	1000 (approx)
Sumburgh d	1130
Fair Isle a	1410 (approx)

Alternate Thu

Fair Isle d	0600
Lerwick a	1030 (approx)
Lerwick d	1515
Fair Isle a	1945 (approx)

All bookings to J W Stout Tel. 01595 760222 
and must be confirmed 24 hrs before departure.


</pre>
<H3>FOULA SERVICE</H3>
<pre>
2nd May to 19th September 1996

Tue/alternate Thu

Foula d	0930
Walls d	1430

Saturdays

Foula d	0930
Walls d	1330

Alternate Thu (commencing 9th May)

Foula     d	0800
Scalloway d	1330

All bookings to R Holbourn Tel. 01595 753232 
and must be confirmed 24 hrs before departure.


</pre>
<H3>PAPA STOUR SERVICE</H3>
<pre>
Mon/Wed/Fri/Sat

West Burrafirth d	0900
Papa Stour      d	1000

Fri/Sat/Sun

West Burrafirth d	1800
Papa Stour      d	1900

All bookings to T Gray Tel. 01595 873227 
and must be confirmed 24 hours before departure. 	
Bookings: T. Gray (Tel. 01595 873227) 
	


   All bookings should be confirmed 24 hours before departure. 
   ON ALL FERRY SERVICES BOOKED VEHICLES MUST BE AT THE 
      TERMINAL FlVE MINUTES PRIOR TO DEPARTURE TIME.
BOOKINGS FOR LATE NIGHT RUNS MUST BE RECEIVED BY 1700 THE EVENING BEFORE.

For information on all Inter-Island services Tel. 01426 986763.


SHETLAND ISLANDS COUNCIL
ROADS AND TRANSPORT DEPARTMENT, GRANTFIELD, LERWICK. 
TEL: 01595 692024 
</pre>

