</HEAD>
<BODY><BODY BACKGROUND="/pics/parch.gif">
<center>
<IMG SRC="/pics/header.gif">

<P>
<H1>Writers and Poets Page</H1>

<HR>
<H2>
New Writing at The Shetland News</H2>

<H4>In this section we will feature some of the best new writing<BR> from Shetland and the Shetland &quot;diaspora&quot;.
<BR><P>
<HR>
<BR>

<H3>
If you would like to submit work for consideration,<BR> then please <A href="mailto:jonathan.wills@zetnet.co.uk"><img src="/pics/bigemail.gif" alt="E-mail" align=middle></A> the Editor.
</H3>





<HR>
<P>
Exclusive to The Shetland News
<P>
<A HREF="mairi/mairi.html">New poetry from Mairi MacMillan</A>
<P>


<HR>
<P>
On 24th November the Unst Writers Group launched their second anthology of poems and prose,<BR> &quot;More Hamar Nights&quot;, featuring the work of a dozen writers,<br> mostly based in the island of Unst.
<P>
The group meets once a month<BR> in the winter at Little Hamar, Baltasound. 
<BR>
Members set themselves themes or topics for the following month<BR> and read out what they've done.
<P>
By kind permission of the publishers we present three samples <BR>from &quot;More Hamar Nights&quot;, <br>available in paperback from the publishers or local booksellers at  &#163;5.99.
<P>
Contact address and number:
<P>
Unst Writers Group<BR>
Hamar<BR>
BALTASOUND<BR>
Unst<BR>
Shetland ZE2 9DS<BR>
Tel: +44 (0)1957 711695<BR>
</H4>
<BR>


<P>
<H3><A HREF="hamar/hamar.html">Poems from the new book &quot;More Hamar Nights&quot;</A></H3>
<BR>
by members of the Unst Writers' Group

</center>
<P>

<HR>

Words strictly Copyright of the authors concerned. 


<HR>


