<BR>
Homepage of the Shetland Entomological Group
<BR>

<P>
<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/insects/review.html">Insects in general</a>
<BR>
A review of all the insect groups recorded in Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/insects/moth.html">Moths in Shetland</a>
<BR>
A review of all moths occurring in Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/insects/butfly94.html">Butterflies in Shetland</a>
<BR>
A review of all butterfly occurrences in Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/insects/hover.html">Shetland Hoverflies</a>
<BR>
A review of all the hoverfly occurrences in Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/insects/dragon.html">Shetland Dragonflies</a>
<BR>
A review of the Dragonfly occurrences in Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/insects/wasps.html">Common Wasp colonisation</a>
<BR>
The story of the common wasp colonisation of Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/moluscs/">Non-marine Molluscs</a>
<BR>
A review of all the slugs and snails occurring in Shetland
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.dmu.ac.uk/~jafowler/shetres.html">De Montfort University</a>
<BR>
Research Projects in Shetland by Jim Fowler
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.gla.ac.uk/~gbza22/foula4.html">Birds of Foula</a>
<BR>
The Birds of Foula by Kenny Ensor at Glasgow University
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/braer/">Wildlife effects of the Braer</a>
<BR>
The impact on Shetland's wildlife from the Braer oil spill
<BR>

<P>

<A HREF="http://www.zetnet.co.uk/sigs/ponies/">The Shetland Pony</A>
<BR>
Information about the Shetland Pony and Shetland breeders
<BR>

<P>

<a href="http://www.magicnet.net/~michon/">Michon Shelties</a>
<BR>
Shetland Sheepdogs Information Pages
<BR>



</UL>
</UL>
</UL>

