http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/shipping/freights/freights.html 194.72.245.173 19970110110555 text/html 3375
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 11:06:01 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 3204
Last-modified: Sun, 25 Aug 1996 21:56:30 GMT
