<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/runway/runway.html 194.72.245.173 19970110121238 text/html 7244
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:12:42 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 7073
Last-modified: Thu, 07 Nov 1996 00:16:00 GMT
