<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/fertilise/fertilise.html 194.72.245.173 19970110121431 text/html 4154
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:14:34 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
