<DOCNO>WT12-B39-96</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA092-000991-B035-9</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/swept/swept.html 194.72.245.173 19970110122025 text/html 4603
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:19:55 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
