<DOCOLDNO>IA092-000991-B035-130</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/yell/yell.html 194.72.245.173 19970110122157 text/html 4795
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:21:56 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
