<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/fiesta/fiesta.html 194.72.245.173 19970110122723 text/html 2293
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:27:21 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 2122
Last-modified: Wed, 16 Oct 1996 21:26:08 GMT
