<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/suspense/suspense.html 194.72.245.173 19970110122756 text/html 3746
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:27:59 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
