<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/critics/critics.html 194.72.245.173 19970110123942 text/html 4278
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:39:45 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 4107
Last-modified: Thu, 26 Sep 1996 22:48:56 GMT
