http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/appeal/appeal.html 194.72.245.173 19970110124230 text/html 6224
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:42:30 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 6053
Last-modified: Tue, 24 Sep 1996 20:00:23 GMT
