<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Shetland News - Svein Ove Ask rowing to Norway
   </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="/pics/parch.gif">
<center>
<IMG SRC="/pics/header.gif">

<P>
<H1>  Follow Svein Ove Ask's attempted route  </H1>
<H2>  to Norway on his solo, 180 mile row </H2>
<img SRC="/pics/ftt6.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt7.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt8.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt9.gif">
<img SRC="/pics/ftt0.gif">
<HR>
<P>
</center>
<P>
Clicking on the map below will give you a bigger version.

<P>
<A HREF="map15.jpg"><IMG SRC="map15s.jpg" align=left HSPACE=5 VSPACE=10></A>
<A HREF="svein9.jpg"><IMG SRC="svein9s.jpg" ALIGN=right HSPACE=5 VSPACE=10></A>

<BR clear=all>

