<DOCHDR>
http://www.shetland-news.co.uk:80/headline/svein/svein.html 194.72.245.173 19970110124619 text/html 3913
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 12:46:23 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 3742
Last-modified: Wed, 18 Sep 1996 23:22:55 GMT
