<P>

<P>
Important:<BR>

<P>
All fares quoted are single unless otherwise stated and are inclusive
of dues levied by the respective Harbour authorities.<BR>

<P>
For return fares, double the amounts shown.<BR>

<P>
All fares shown take account of current HM Goverment Subvention
<P>
