<P>
<B>Round Trips<BR>
</B>
<P>
Aberdeen - Stromness - Scabster &amp; vice versa
<P>
Aberdeen - Lerwick - Stromness - Aberdeen &amp; vice versa
<P>
Scrabster - Stromness - Lerwick - Stromness - Scrabster
<P>
Aberdeen - Lerwick - Stromness - Scrabster &amp; vice versa<BR>

<P>
To calculate round trip passenger fares, simply add together the
single fares shown on these pages applicable to the routes on
which you will be travelling.
