<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Lerwick Harbour Trust - Home Page</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<!-- <BODY BACKGROUND="lhtparch.jpg"> -->
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFEF2">
<center>
<IMG SRC="lhtlogo.gif">

<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>

<h1>Welcome to 'Britain's Top Port'</h1>
</CENTER>
<CENTER><img width=600 height=3 src="lhtstrip.gif"></CENTER>


<P><BR>
<CENTER>
<H2>
<STRONG>Lerwick Harbour is Shetland's international port</STRONG><BR>at the crossroads of the north-east Atlantic
</H2>
</CENTER>


<P><A HREF="harbour.jpg"><IMG SRC="harbours.jpg" align=left HSPACE=10 vspace=25 BORDER=0></A><BR> <BR> 
<BR> <BR> <BR> 
<UL><LI><A HREF="oilrelated/oilrelated.html">Logistics base</A> for the offshore oil industry.
<P> <BR>
<LI>Major British <A HREF="fishing/fishing.html">fishing port</A>.
<P> <BR>

<LI>Shetland's main general <A HREF="cargo/cargo.html">cargo port</A>.
<P> <BR>

<LI>Popular destination on <A HREF="tourism/tourism.html">cruise ships and leisure craft</A>.

</UL><BR clear=all>

<CENTER><img width=80% height=3 src="lhtstrip.gif"></CENTER>

<P>
The anchorage in Bressay Sound is big, deep and sheltered. Twin entrances, tugs, pilots and radar assist safe, 24-hour access to <A HREF="information/information.html">deepwater quays</A>, all year round. 
<P>

First-class shoreside  <A HREF="information/phonenos.html">services</A> include agency and Customs, ship repair and maintenance, dry-docking, a modern fishmarket and fish processing plants, meeting the highest European standards.
<P>
A traditional Shetland welcome awaits you at the gateway to <A HREF="http://www.shetland-tourism.co.uk/">these fascinating islands</A>. 
<P>
If, after looking at the other pages, you want to know more about Britain's Top Port, or discuss any detailed requirements in confidence, please <A HREF="mailto:lkharbour@lht.zetnet.co.uk">email us</A> today.
<P>
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<CENTER><img width=600 height=3 src="lhtstrip.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
These pages &copy; <A HREF="mailto:lkharbour@lht.zetnet.co.uk">Lerwick Harbour Trust</A>, Shetland, 1996.

<P>
Please report any problems with these pages to the <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@shetland-news.co.uk"><I>Webmaster</I></a>. Thank you.
<BR>
<B>Web Authoring</B> and 
<B>Web Site Maintenance</B> by <A HREF="http://www.shetland-news.co.uk">The Shetland News</A>
<BR>
<B>Web Site Space</B> from <A HREF="http://www.zetnet.co.uk">Zetnet Services Ltd</A>
</FONT>
</BODY>
