<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Lerwick Harbour Trust</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFEF2">
<center>
<IMG SRC="lhtlogo.gif">

<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>
<H1>Technical Details</H1>

</center>
<P>
<CENTER><img width=600 height=3 src="lhtstrip.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<A NAME="one"></a><CENTER><B><H2>Quays, Docks and Berths</H2></B></CENTER>

<P>
<CENTER><img width=600 height=3 src="lhtstrip.gif"></CENTER>
<P>
<IMG SRC="laurenson.gif" align=left hspace=10 vspace=5 border=0 alt="Diagram of the berths available">


<H3><STRONG><P>Laurenson Quay
<BR>Alexandra Wharf
<BR>Albert Dock
<BR>Victoria Pier Breakwater</STRONG></H3>

<P><STRONG>Depth:</STRONG> 3m-9m
<BR><STRONG>Length of quay: </STRONG>900m
<BR><STRONG>Services:</STRONG> Fish Market
<BR>Water, Telephone, Electricity
<BR>Visiting Yacht Berthing
<BR>Garbage Disposal

<BR clear=all>
<P>
<CENTER><img width=350 height=3 src="lhtstrip.gif"></CENTER>

