Personal Programs in cooperation with Thomas Cook Publishing (UK), the European
Railplanner brings schedules, approximate fares, and general information for
hundreds of the most popular European rail routes into a fun, informative
Windows environment.  It's the perfect PC companion to the famous
<A HREF="http://www.eurodata.com/tcookbk.htm">Thomas Cook European Timetable</A>.
 If you're doing Europe by rail, the <B>Railplanner</B> makes itinerary design
a snap.  You can easily import routes from <B>Railplanner</B> into your <B>EuroData</B>
itinerary.   Estimated MSRP: $29.95.  <I>Availability To Be Announced</I></P>
<HR><IMG SRC="http://www.eurodata.com/redevs.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
