<P><I>Welcome to the second online edition of <I>European Visits</I>.  We
hope you'll enjoy the fine collection of European travel articles we've gathered
here, and we hope you'll come back often -- new articles will appear regularly. 
If you're interested in contributing to <I>European Visits</I>, please check
out our <A HREF="http://www.eurodata.com/edvsubmt.htm">submission guidelines</A>
here on the 'Net.  Also, see our new
<A HREF="http://www.eurodata.com/classads.htm">Classified Ads</A> section --
you can post questions, find travel partners, locate European apartments for
rent, or tell others about your own travel product or service.</I></P>
<HR>
<P><B>Special Offer!</B>  Through July 1996 we are offering <B>free</B>
1-year (6 issue) subscriptions to the print edition of <B><I>European Visits</I></B>.
 Just E-Mail your complete postal address <A HREF="mailto:eurodata@nas.com">here</A>
with &quot;Subscribe EV&quot; in the message heading.  <I>Valid for United
States addresses only.</I></P>
