<H6><I><FONT COLOR="#000000">Advertisement</FONT></I></H6>
<H1><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Hotel F&uuml;rstenhof Wien</FONT></H1>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">Neubauguertel 4, A-1070 Wien</FONT><BR></H2>
<P><B>Built at the beginning of the 20th century, the Hotel F&uuml;rstenhof is
one of the last really old family-owned hotels in Vienna, now under the care of
a third generation of ownership.  Ideally situated opposite the Westbahnhof rail
station, on Vienna's main shopping street and convenient to all public
transportation, the Hotel F&uuml;rstenhof offers rooms with private bath/shower
from ATS 880, along with very economical rooms with shared bath from ATS 500. 
<I>(1 US $ = approx. 10 ATS, April 1996) 
</I> Rates are per night and include breakfast buffet, telephone, minibar, and
cable-TV; modem connections available on request. </B><BR></P>
