<P>Want to do the BIG tour at a little price?  <B>Contiki</B>'s <I>Winter
Highlights</I> uses 13 days to visit <B>London</B>, <B>Paris</B>, <B>Lucerne</B>,
<B>Florence</B>, <B>Venice</B>, <B>Munich</B>, and <B>Amsterdam</B> &#151;
then ends with a week of <FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">skiing</FONT> in the <B>Austrian
Alps</B>.  The 20-day package starts at $1550 PP/DO, including air; through
mid-February.  <B>800-CONTIKI.</B>  
