have obtained exclusive permission to bring tour groups into the <I>Hall of
Facets</I> in the <B>Kremlin</B>; normally off-limits, this was the
<FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">Czar's throne room</FONT> and has been the setting for
many historic meetings of world leaders.  The hall, lined with frescoes and
flanked by elaborately carved portals, is also considered one of the most
<FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">beautiful</FONT> rooms in the Moscow complex.  General
Tours offers a variety of packages geared to this and other top notch sights in
Russia; prices start at $2849 including air.  <B>800-221-2216</B>.  
