a toll-free (US) number.  A computerized system will read your messages to you
over the phone and take down your reply as digitized dictation.  Other options
can let you access voicemail, <FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">faxes</FONT>, and news &amp;
weather reports.  <B>800-432-6169</B>.  
