<P>Of course we all know that <I>nothing</I> ever <FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">goes
wrong when you travel</FONT>.  But if it ever did, you'd be glad to have
<I>Trouble Free Travel</I>, a new book from <B>Nolo Press</B>.  Written by two
travel attorneys, the $14.95 volume focuses on your rights as a traveler&#151;and
how to avoid getting them <FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">trampled</FONT> by an airline,
hotel, tour operator, or anyone else.  Order from Nolo Press, <B>800-992-6656</B>.
