rates considerably lower than travelers pay if they rent in Eastern countries. 
<STRONG>800 223 5555</STRONG>.<BR><BR></LI>
<LI>Are you due for a special treat?  The <STRONG>H&ocirc;tel Meurice</STRONG>,
