taxes and visa fees extra.  <STRONG>800-526-4927</STRONG>.<BR><BR></LI>
<LI>Planning to visit <STRONG>Greece</STRONG>, but bored with fancy hotels? 
You can charter a fully-crewed yacht for your stay at about the same cost,
according to Valef Yachts S.A.  Get more information at <STRONG>800- 223-3845</STRONG>.

</LI></UL>
