can walk 2-5 hour trails. The cottage is on the top of the hill, with a lovely
view.  The house is comprising of two bedrooms,  a kitchen fully equipped, ready
for self catering, and a bathroom.   The price is DM 25 per head/day all
inclusive.   For booking e-mail <A HREF="mailto:fari@ilink.nis.za.">fari@ilink.nis.za.
</A>
</P><IMG SRC="http://www.eurodata.com/evline.gif">
<P><B>ATTRACTIVE CENTRAL FLAT IN EDINBURGH</B>. Pleasant, clean and
comfortable with generous facilities.  Sleeps five.   Car parking.  Frequent
buses. Things to see &amp; do: the Scottish Experience, wonderful 4 course
banquet;  American football; Scottish Claymores Entertaining Ghost Walks; secret
hidden medieval city;  Maid of the Forth cruises; Deep Sea World,  museums, art
galleries,  zoo and lots more.  E-mail
<A HREF="mailto:Marjory@hana.demon.co.uk">Marjory@hana.demon.co.uk</A></P><IMG
SRC="http://www.eurodata.com/evline.gif">
<P><BR><I><B><FONT COLOR="#FFFF00">Tour Operators / Guides
</FONT></B></I><BR></P>
<P><B>EUROPE BY PRIVATE CAR WITH AN EXPERIENCED GUIDE/CHAUFFEUR</B> is a lot
more fun than going by bus.  Two all-inclusive weeks except trans-Atlantic air,
for four people is $2240 per person using a spacious, comfortable Renault Espace
and charming country inns.  Email John Kluft at
<A HREF="mailto:jkluft@telis.org">jkluft@telis.org</A> or call him at <B>(916)
926-2350</B> and he will give you all the details and references you need. 
</P><IMG SRC="http://www.eurodata.com/evline.gif">
